billingStatementsDesc: View your billing history and retrieve past invoices or faktur pajak (tax receipts) when payment has been made.
feesListedAre: Fee listed are per transaction in Indonesian Rupiah (IDR) and not including VAT (10% from fee).
phFeesListedAre: Fees listed are per transaction and are exclusive of 12% VAT.
payNowModalInfoText: Choose your preferred payment option to settle outstanding fees.
billingWalletInfoText: Funds in the wallet will be automatically deducted to pay any outstanding fees, starting from the oldest unpaid invoice.
transferBalanceInfoText: Transfer available funds from your cash balance to your billing wallet to pay any outstanding fees automatically.
payInvoicesIntro: To top up your balance and pay your invoice(s), transfer money to one of the bank accounts below.
payInvoicesNotice: <0>Important!</0> Partial payment of an invoice is not available. Any excess payment will remain in your balance until your next full invoice payment.
